room_title: Escape room "Cosmic Collision" by Time Travel Escapes in West Palm Beach
room_description: We are looking for an elite team of NASA Scientists to travel into the future to save our world. In the research lab, you will need to find all the information needed to determine the fate of our earth. Make your way through the laser security and figure out how to activate the laser beam to destroy the meteor that will collide with Earth. Come help us prevent the mass destruction of our planet!
